# Video Placeholder

Place your video.mp4 file in this directory.

The video should be:
- Named: video.mp4
- Format: MP4 (H.264 codec recommended)
- Duration: 3-10 seconds (for looping)
- Resolution: 1080p or higher
- Optimized for web (compressed)

The video will autoplay, loop, and be muted by default for better user experience.